# lssr

Alternative ls command.

[![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/lssr)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/lssr)
[![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/lssr)](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/lssr)
